text:
Natalia Murek (born 8 September 1999) is a Polish volleyball player.
Career.
She played at the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, 2017 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2018 Montreux Volley Masters, 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League, and 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. She played for Volley Wrocław.
